name: Ryckert Chomp
description:
Made this in a day or two, meant to make it a clicker with bananas and other things with the ultimate goal being to eat the moon.

This is my first unity project and it was tough figuring out a bunch of stuff but I was so proud of my progress that I wanted to upload.

Hopefully next time there is a game jam I won't have work and school competing for my time as well!
